title: New York nanny accused of killing 2 children heads to court
text:
New York nanny accused of killing 2 children heads to court 6:59am EST - 01:44 
A New York nanny accused of stabbing to death two children in her care heads to a Manhattan courtroom on Thursday for opening statements in her trial for the 2012 killing. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
